<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/hr-head') %>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/hr-navbar') %>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hr-hero text-white py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-7">
        <h1 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="font-size:2.2rem;">
          🐎 Türkiye'nin At Yarışı<br>Tahmin & Analiz Platformu
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-4 opacity-85" style="font-size:1.05rem; max-width:540px;">
          TJK günlük programı, AGF tabloları, yarış bülteni ve sonuçlarını
          tek platformda takip edin. Kupon oluşturun, tahminlerinizi geliştirin.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/program" class="btn btn-light text-hr-green fw-bold px-4">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days me-2"></i>Günlük Program
          </a>
          <a href="/bulten" class="btn px-4 fw-bold" style="background:#c8a400; color:#1a1a1e; border:none;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-newspaper me-2"></i>Bülteni Gör
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex gap-3 mt-4 flex-wrap">
          <span class="badge py-2 px-3" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); font-size:0.8rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check me-1"></i>TJK Resmi Verisi
          </span>
          <span class="badge py-2 px-3" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); font-size:0.8rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate me-1"></i>Günlük Güncelleme
          </span>
          <span class="badge py-2 px-3" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15); font-size:0.8rem;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock-open me-1"></i>Ücretsiz
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 d-none d-lg-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="text-center" style="font-size:8rem; opacity:0.25;">🏇</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Hızlı Erişim Kartları -->
<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row g-4">

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <a href="/program" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width:50px;height:50px;background:#e8f5ec;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days fa-lg" style="color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Yarış Programı</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
              Günlük TJK koşu programı, at listeleri, jokey bilgileri ve ikramiyeler.
            </p>
            <span class="btn btn-sm" style="background:#1a6b3a; color:#fff;">Programa Git <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <a href="/bulten" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width:50px;height:50px;background:#fff8e1;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-newspaper fa-lg" style="color:#c8a400;"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Günlük Bülten</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
              Detaylı at bilgileri, performans verileri, soy ağacı ve son derece bilgileri.
            </p>
            <span class="btn btn-sm" style="background:#c8a400; color:#1a1a1e;">Bültene Git <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <a href="/agf" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width:50px;height:50px;background:#e3f2fd;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-bar fa-lg" style="color:#0d6efd;"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">AGF Tablosu</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
              Anlaşmalı Ganyan Fiyatları — favori atları belirleyin, tahminlerinizi güçlendirin.
            </p>
            <span class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">AGF'ye Git <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <a href="/sonuclar" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width:50px;height:50px;background:#fff3cd;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-trophy fa-lg" style="color:#fd7e14;"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Yarış Sonuçları</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
              Günlük koşu sonuçları, derece süreleri, ganyan ve ikramiye ödemeleri.
            </p>
            <span class="btn btn-sm btn-warning">Sonuçlara Git <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <a href="/kupon-hesaplama" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width:50px;height:50px;background:#fce4ec;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-calculator fa-lg" style="color:#dc3545;"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Kupon Hesaplama</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
              3'lü, 4'lü, 5'li ve 6'lı ganyan kupon ücretlerini kolayca hesaplayın.
            </p>
            <span class="btn btn-sm btn-danger">Hesapla <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <a href="/veri-bilgisi" class="text-decoration-none">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
          <div class="card-body p-4">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width:50px;height:50px;background:#f3e5f5;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info fa-lg" style="color:#6f42c1;"></i>
              </div>
              <h5 class="mb-0 fw-bold">Veri Bülten Bilgisi</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
              Verilerimizin kaynağı, güncelleme saatleri ve bülten içerikleri hakkında bilgi.
            </p>
            <span class="btn btn-sm" style="background:#6f42c1; color:#fff;">Bilgi Al <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- Hakkında -->
<section style="background:#f8f9fa;" class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="color:#1a6b3a;">Neden bankotahminleri.com?</h2>
        <ul class="list-unstyled">
          <li class="mb-3 d-flex gap-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mt-1" style="color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
            <span><strong>TJK Resmi Verisi</strong> — Türkiye Jokey Kulübü'nün resmi API'sinden anlık veri</span>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-3 d-flex gap-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mt-1" style="color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
            <span><strong>Tüm Hipodromlar</strong> — Ankara, İstanbul, İzmir, Bursa ve diğer tüm pistler</span>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-3 d-flex gap-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mt-1" style="color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
            <span><strong>Detaylı At Bilgileri</strong> — AGF, jokey, antrenör, soy bilgisi, son performans</span>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-3 d-flex gap-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mt-1" style="color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
            <span><strong>Kupon Hesaplayıcı</strong> — 3'lü'den 6'lı'ya tüm bahis türleri için hesaplama</span>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-3 d-flex gap-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check mt-1" style="color:#1a6b3a;"></i>
            <span><strong>Tamamen Ücretsiz</strong> — Kayıt olmadan tüm verilere erişin</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-3 border" style="background:#fff; border-color:#dee2e6 !important;">
          <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="color:#1a6b3a;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-exclamation me-2" style="color:#fd7e14;"></i>Yasal Uyarı
          </h6>
          <p style="font-size:0.875rem; color:#6c757d; line-height:1.7; margin:0;">
            bankotahminleri.com bir bahis sitesi değildir. Sunulan tüm veriler
            TJK resmi kaynağından alınmakta olup yalnızca bilgilendirme ve
            analiz amacı taşımaktadır. At yarışı bahisleri yasal düzenlemeler
            kapsamında yalnızca TJK bayileri ve resmi kanallar aracılığıyla
            oynanabilir. Bahis oynamak için yasal yaşta olmanız gerekmektedir.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/hr-footer') %>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<style>
.hover-card { transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s; }
.hover-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1) !important; }
</style>
</body>
</html>
